name: Wild Country Classic Rock Set 1-10
description: A tried-and-true design for trusted placements. The convex side locks the nut into place against the 2-contact point of the concave side, creating a stable wedge. Side tapers assist in wedging in sideways placements.Classic nut geometry fits in most constrictions.6064 aluminum with steel cables.Hollow extrusion in size 7-10 reduces weight.Includes Wild Country Classic Rocks sizes 1 to 10.
